metadata.name: never ever
metadata.description:
Never ever is a bitter pill,
A wound that won't heal, a void to fill.
But it can be a chance to start anew,
To find new dreams, and to follow through.

So let us not fear the words "never ever",
For they can be a call to be clever.
To learn from our mistakes, and to grow,
And to find new paths where we can go.
